1 DATE November 1934
1 PLAC Powell, South Dakota
1 _DSCR Obituary for Mary Elizabeth Hall
1 _META <metadataxml><content><line>&lt;p&gt;Mary Elizabeth Hall was born January 1, 1860, in Memphis, Missouri and died in Powell, South Dakota November 1, 1934 at the age of seventy-four years. &amp;nbsp;She was married to Isaac Colvin, October 9, 1879 a
2 CONC t the age of 20. &amp;nbsp;The family lived in Missouri until 1910, going to Haakon County where they resided on a homestead nine miles north of Powell. &amp;nbsp;In 1929 she and her husband moved to Powell and she resided there with him until he
2 CONC r death. &amp;nbsp;She had nine children, one having died in infancy. &amp;nbsp;Funeral services were held from the Sacred Heart church in Philip, South Dakota with a solemn Requiem Mass.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;-informatio
2 CONC n taken from obituary found in Forrester-Colvin family Bible held by Ronald Colvin&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</line></content></metadataxml>
